text: Ærest on cyselburnan on ðone ham of ðam hamme andlang streames.
To hwitan wyllon of hwitan willon ondlang streames to forda of ðam forda to herpoðe of herpoðe to þære hege ræwe þonone to herpoðe andlang herpoðes an furlang.
Þis is þara þreora gyrda land boc æt Ceosol burnan þe Eadgar cing hætð gebocod Wulfhearde on ece yrfe.
